'''Poovulagin Nanbargal''' is an environmental organization based in [[Tamil nadu]], India.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.thehindu.com/features/metroplus/a-network-for-nature/article4594605.ece |title=A network for Nature - The Hindu |publisher=M.thehindu.com |date= |accessdate=2017-08-28}}</ref> It spearheaded legal battle against [[Kudankulam Nuclear Power Plant]].<ref>http://archives.deccanchronicle.com/130718/news-current-affairs/article/first-bench-hear-pil-kudankulam-nulcear-power-plant</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/antikudankulam-activists-to-raise-protest-to-next-level/article5032106.ece |title=Anti-Kudankulam activists to raise protest to next level - The Hindu |publisher=M.thehindu.com |date= |accessdate=2017-08-28}}</ref>
